title: U.S. wind power generation 2000 to 2018
yAxis: Net generation in billion kilowatt hours
summary: In general Net generation in billion kilowatt hours has rose over the Year.
Net generation in billion kilowatt hours is roughly constant from 2002 to 2003, gradually increasing from 2003 to 2012, and finally roughly constant from 2012 to 2017.
The highest Net generation in billion kilowatt hours, of value 254.3 was reached at Year 2017
The lowest Net generation in billion kilowatt hours, of value 10.35 was reported at Year 2002
